6\u201317 UEFA Europa League#Third qualifying round|3QR]]\n| {{flagicon|CZE}} [[FK Mlad\u00e1 Boleslav|Mlad\u00e1 Boleslav]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#dfd;\"| 2\u20130\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#fdd;\"| 0\u20131\n| style=\"text-align:center;| '''2\u20131'''\n| [[File:Symbol keep vote.svg|17px]]\n|-\n| [[2016\u201317 UEFA Europa League#Play-off round|PO]]\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} [[KAA Gent|Gent]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#fdd;\"| 0\u20134\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#fdd;\"| 1\u20132\n| style=\"text-align:center;| '''1\u20136'''\n| [[File:Symbol delete vote.svg|17px]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2017\u201318\n| rowspan=\"4\"| [[2017\u201318 UEFA Europa League|UEFA Europa League]]\n| [[2017\u201318 UEFA Europa League#First qualifying round|1QR]]\n| {{flagicon|MDA}} [[FC Dacia Chi\u0219in\u0103u|Dacia]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#dfd;\"| 3\u20130\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#dfd;\"| 4\u20130\n| style=\"text-align:center;| '''7\u20130'''\n| [[File:Symbol keep vote.svg|17px]]\n|-\n| [[2017\u201318 UEFA Europa League#Second qualifying round|2QR]]\n| {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Helsingin Jalkapalloklubi|HJK]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#dfd;\"| 3\u20131\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffd;\"| 1\u20131\n| style=\"text-align:center;| '''4\u20132'''\n| [[File:Symbol keep vote.svg|17px]]\n|-\n| [[2017\u201318 UEFA Europa League#Third qualifying round|3QR]]\n| {{flagicon|LTU}} [[FK Trakai|Trakai]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#dfd;\"| 3\u20130\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#fdd;\"| 1\u20132\n| style=\"text-align:center;| '''4\u20132'''\n| [[File:Symbol keep vote.svg|17px]]\n|-\n| [[2017\u201318 UEFA Europa League#Play-off round|PO]]\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[AC Milan|Milan]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#fdd;\"| 0\u20131\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#fdd;\"| 0\u20136\n| style=\"text-align:center;| '''0\u20137'''\n| [[File:Symbol delete vote.svg