 Glico Features JKT48 | ref = {{harvid|Susilo 2013}}}}\n* {{Cite news | last = Tobing | first = Ramadan | title = JKT48 Sukses Menggelar Konser Amal Bagi Korban Banjir Jakarta | url = http://rollingstone.co.id/read/2013/01/30/113141/2156124/1093/jkt48-sukses-menggelar-konser-amal-bagi-korban-banjir-jakarta | work = Rolling Stone Indonesia | publisher = a&e Media | date = 30 January 2013 | accessdate = 7 February 2013 | language = Indonesian | trans-title = JKT48 Holds Successful Charity Concert for Victims of Jakarta Flood | ref = {{Harvid|Tobing 2013}} | url-status = dead | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130224064331/http://rollingstone.co.id/read/2013/01/30/113141/2156124/1093/jkt48-sukses-menggelar-konser-amal-bagi-korban-banjir-jakarta | archivedate = 24 February 2013 | df = dmy-all }}\n{{Refend}}\n\n'''Web sources'''\n{{Refbegin|1}}\n* {{Cite web | script-title=ja:\u7d44\u95a3\u5f8c\u65b0\u4f53\u5236 | url = http://www.akb48.co.jp/news/detail.php?id=7929 | publisher = AKS | date = 24 August 2012 | accessdate = 8 February 2013 | language = Japanese |trans-title=Post-Reorganization Lineup | ref = {{Harvid|AKS 2012}}}}\n* {{Cite web | title = Apa Itu AKB48 | url = http://jkt48.com/about/akb48 | publisher = JKT48 Operation Team | accessdate = 7 February 2013 | language = Indonesian |trans-title=What Is AKB48? | ref = {{Harvid|JKT48 Operation Team, Apa Itu AKB48}}}}\n* {{Cite web | title = Pengunduran Rilis CD Perdana JKT48 | url = http://jkt48.com/news/detail/id/113 | publisher = JKT48 Operation Team | date = 1 February 2013 | accessdate = 1 February 2013 | language = Indonesian |trans-title=Release of JKT48's First CD Delayed | ref = {{Harvid|JKT48 Operation Team 2013, Pengunduran Rilis CD Perdana JKT48}}}}\n* {{Cite web|title=Profil Anggota |url=http://bagaimana-cara.net/member-jkt48-terseksi/ |publisher=JKT48 Operation Team |accessdate=3 November 2011 |language=Indonesian |trans-title=Member Profiles |ref={{Harvid|JKT48 Operation Team, Profil Anggota